title: Are You Holding Your Vote?
itunes:title: Are You Holding Your Vote?
description:
Today on the show we opened up the phone lines to see what our listeners thought about Diddy's comments on holding his vote until he see's a black agenda from Joe Biden, which many were upset about. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Kentucky governor for not double checking on his responsibility and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
